(T1 dark-brown anteriorly in 
<taxonomicName authority="Ferrari, 2019" authorityName="Ferrari" authorityYear="2019" box="[804,962,189,215]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sertanicola" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[804,962,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">C. sertanicola</emphasis>
